description.@value:
Cheerful and stylish non-smoking apartment, completely renovated; Size: 36 m2; Located on the 2nd floor of our house; 
Cozy kitchen-living room featuring comfortable seating area, well-equipped kitchen unit (4-plate stove incl. oven, dish washer, fridge with freezer, a full range of cooking utensils, coffee machine, toaster, spice rack, kettle), double couch, SAT-TV and radio incl. MC/CD player;
Comfortable triple bedroom, furnished with wood furniture, equipped with SAT-TV and room safe;
Bright bath room with shower and toilet, located right next to the bedroom; 
West-facing balcony, size: 9 m2; perfectly suited for spending some hours in the afternoon sun
